Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.05,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}UN-DELAYED, Oh my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:18.93,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}UN-DELAYED, Fallin' fallin' love now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:24.48,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}それが運命…Oh my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:32.11,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}聞こえないなんて言わせないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.65,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}1,2…heart beat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:37.45,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}星の海でひとつきりの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:40.99,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}私だけの運命かもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.41,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}本気で愛したら　どうするの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:43.45,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs14}(君は)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:47.33,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一生懸命なこころで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:50.67,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}探していた未来のありかを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:58.51,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君の中に見つけたんだ　消えない夢のありか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:04.39,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}もしも世界が一日止まるならば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.77,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs14}(止まる時には)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:11.81,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}私をずっとずっと抱きしめていて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.81,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs14}(抱きしめてよね)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:15.03,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我が儘なこと考えてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.82,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ごめんね…好きは「無限大」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:22.74,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}明日を　恐れたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.07,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs14}(1,2 heart!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.49,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs14}(1,2 beat!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.99,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}気持ち確かめたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:26.70,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs14}(UN-DELAYED)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:34.29,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}触れた指先　熱い奇跡を受けとめてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.30,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}UN-DELAYED, Oh my love!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.05,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}UN-DELAYED, Oh my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:18.93,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}UN-DELAYED, Fallin' fallin' love now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:24.48,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}这就是命中注定…Oh my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:32.11,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不会让你说你没听见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.65,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}1,2…heart beat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:37.45,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在星辰大海中唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:40.99,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只属于我的命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.41,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}若是动了真情  怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:43.45,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(你又会)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:47.33,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用尽全心全意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:50.67,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去寻找未来的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:58.51,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在你那里找到了  不会消去的梦之所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:04.39,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}假如世界停转一天的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.77,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(在停转之时)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:11.81,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}请一直一直抱紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.81,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(紧紧抱着我)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:15.03,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}尽想着这些任性的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.82,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}对不起…喜欢你「没有极限」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:22.74,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不要害怕  明天的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.07,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(1,2 heart!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.49,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(1,2 beat!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.99,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}希望可以确认你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:26.70,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(UN-DELAYED)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:34.29,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用触及的指尖接受我热情的奇迹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.30,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}UN-DELAYED, Oh my love!
